headline.main: Tree Falls, Kills Woman at National Park in California
headline.print_headline: Tree Falls, Kills Woman at National Park in California

lead_paragraph: Officials say a 21-year-old woman was killed by a falling tree at Half Dome Village in Yosemite National Park.
